/*! \page installation Installation

Download QuantLibXL-bin-0.8.0.exe from the 
<a href="http://sourceforge.net/project/showfiles.php?group_id=12740&package_id=159049">Downloads page</a>.

Run the installer to install QuantLibXL to your system.  To use QuantLibXL;
\li start Excel
\li load the addin - QuantLibXL\\xll\\QuantLibXL-vc80-mt-s-0_8_0.xll
\li load an example workbook e.g. QuantLibXL\\Workbooks\\OriginalExamples\\instruments.xls
\li hit Ctrl-Alt-F9 to refresh the workbook

Send any support queries to quantlib-users@lists.sf.net.

*/
